items.title: VeggieTales Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the VeggieTales Wikia!
items.desc: This Wikia is about the animated children's program VeggieTales. VeggieTales is a series of computer animated children's films featuring anthropomorphic vegetables. Developed by Big Idea, the films convey moral themes based on Christianity spliced with satirical references to pop culture and current events.

items.headline: Welcome to the VeggieTales Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to the VeggieTales - It's For the Kids! Wiki

Join Bob and Larry in VeggieTales, the Christian Biblical show about God!

Come help out by writing and editing articles about characters, episodes, locations songs, etc. If you don't know VeggieTales read this wiki to learn more!

Most of all, have fun!
